@startuml AMR_Swimlane
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam defaultFontColor #2C2C2A
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #5b9bd5
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityBorderThickness 1
skinparam ArrowColor #5F5E5A
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam shadowing false

skinparam swimlane {
    BorderColor #888780
    BorderThickness 1.5
    TitleFontSize 12
    TitleFontStyle bold
    TitleFontColor #2C2C2A
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
}

title <b>AMR System Architecture — Swimlane View</b>\nROS 2 Humble | Mixed Indoor-Outdoor Navigation

|#E1F5EE| <b>Web Interface</b> |
start
:Operator membuka\n**Dashboard**;
note right
  Antarmuka Web
  (browser / mobile)
end note

fork
  :Kirim **Goal / Teleop**\nke Navigation Stack;
fork again
  :Tampilkan **Status Robot**\n& data Odometri;
end fork

|#EEEDFE| <b>Sensor Fusion & Drivers</b> |
:Driver **LiDAR SLLiDAR A2M7**\nmenerima scan 2D;
:Driver **IMU N100**\nmembaca orientasi &\npercepatan;
:Data **Odometri**\nmenerima feedback encoder;

fork
  -> Orientasi / Percepatan;
  :Filter **EKF**\n(Robot Localization);
fork again
  -> Data encoder;
  :Filter **EKF**\n(Robot Localization);
end fork

|#E6F1FB| <b>Navigation Stack (ROS 2 Humble)</b> |
:**SLAM Toolbox & AMCL**\nmembangun peta & lokalisasi;
note right
  Output: Peta (Map) &
  TF transform odom/map
end note

:Terima **Goal / Teleop**\ndari Web Interface;
:Terima **Scan 2D & Obstacle**\ndari LiDAR;
:Terima **Odometri Terfilter**\ndari EKF;

:**Nav2 Stack**\n(Smac Planner · MPPI · Behavior Tree)\nmerencanakan & mengeksekusi path;
note right
  Input: peta + odom + goal
  Output: cmd_vel
end note

:Kirim **cmd_vel**\n(perintah kecepatan)\nke Motor Control;
:Kirim **Status Robot & Odom**\nke Web Interface;

|#FAECE7| <b>Motor Control</b> |
:**USB-to-RS485 Bus**\nmenerima cmd_vel;
note right
  Semua hardware terhubung via
  USB-to-RS485:
  IMU · LiDAR · Driver · Safety
end note

if (Safety Laser **CCF-LAS4-4M**\ndeteksi obstacle < 20 cm?) then (Ya — Darurat)
  :**Hardware Interrupt**\n(Berhenti Darurat)\nlangsung ke RS485;
  note right
    Safety layer independen
    dari Nav2 — interrupt
    tidak melewati Nav2
  end note
  :Motor **BERHENTI**\nsegera;
else (Tidak — Aman)
  :RS485 teruskan\nperintah kontrol;
  :**Motor Driver ZLAC8015D**\nmenerima perintah;
  :**Motor BLDC ZLLG80ASM800**\n(Differential Drive)\nbergerak sesuai cmd_vel;
  :Kirim **Feedback Encoder / Odom**\nke Sensor Fusion;
endif

|#FFF8E7| <b>Power Supply</b> |
:**LiFePO4 Battery**\n(Nominal 48V · Maks 54V);

fork
  -> 48V DC;
  :Suplai daya langsung\nke **Motor Control**;
fork again
  -> 12/19V DC\n(via DC-DC Converter);
  :Suplai daya ke\n**Navigation Stack**\n(komputer / SBC);
end fork

stop

@enduml
